name: Denise LastName
description:
Denise is the fourth in a new set of custom LastName characters, for anyone who wants a consistent character for their SD 1.5 renders.

Denise is a woman in her 30s. She's in great shape, with toned, muscular arms. She's a really fast runner, and she'll swim laps around you given the chance. She has the kind of face you'll want to spend every waking moment trying to make smile. When you do, she'll look at you like you are an idiot, and you will believe that you are an idiot. (None of this will stop you from trying.)

To use this embedding with the Automatic1111 web UI, save the downloaded file to /embeddings/deniselastnamesd15.pt, and then include the trigger word deniselastnamesd15 in your prompt.

(Inspired by Zovya's Nobody series, which is awesome. Go download all of their amazing characters.)

(All of the sample images have full metadata, and were generated with XpucT's Deliberate v2.)
